{
  "texts": [
    "It is hard to overstate the significance of this conclusion.",
    "The conclusion entails that most children born today will witness humanity's disempowerment through AI.",
    "The form of human disempowerment which seems most likely to me is extinction.",
    "As argued earlier, if AI optimizes for some misaligned goal, it will have instrumental reasons to amass as many resources as possible.",
    "AI could plausibly use the resources which humans need to survive (e.g., space) for its own goals."
  ]
}